### File responsibilities
- `graphrag_executor.py` вҖ” orchestrates all 4 stages; the main class `GraphRAGExecutor`
- `prompt_builder.py` вҖ” builds the structured two-section prompt; `PromptBuilder`
- `citation_builder.py` вҖ” resolves chunks + graph findings to page citations; `CitationBuilder`

### Dependencies on existing D2 code
- `src/graph/cypher_queries.py` вҶ’ GRAPHRAG_REASONING templates
- `src/graph/neo4j_builder.py` вҶ’ Neo4j driver, slugify(), confidence_rank()
- `src/retrieval/hybrid_retriever.py` вҶ’ HybridRetriever.search()
- `src/retrieval/dense_retriever.py` вҶ’ DenseRetriever (for expansion scoring)
- `data/sample/sample_chunks.json` вҶ’ chunk store for text lookup

